The movies listed above represent the best-selling porn films of all time.  And as you scroll through them, you’ll probably notice that most are a bit old, some of them released nearly two decades ago.  That being said, these are also some of the most beloved dirty movies ever made and they continue to sell as well today — if not better — than they did the year that they debuted.

You’ll probably also notice that three studios pretty much dominate this list; Wicked Pictures, Digital Playground and Vivid Entertainment.  These two powerhouses of XXX dominated the porn industry for a long time (an argument could be made that Wicked still does) and they absolutely produced some of the most critically acclaimed smut classics of the past generation.

And yeah, having many of the hottest starlets in the business locked up in exclusive contracts for much of this time also helped.

Hopefully, you’ve seen at least half of the films listed above.  Because if you haven’t, your life is a gaping void of meaningless shit.  These smut masterpieces represent everything that is good and great about our civilization and you need them in your life.  Otherwise, what the fuck do you even live for?

